      "content": "it just never stops. the nerves, the burning... it's like being awake inside a fire 24/7. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting to exist when existing just means more of this. sometimes i just stare at the wall and think about how quiet and still everything would be if i just wasn't here anymore. it seems like the only real way to actually get some rest.",
